          <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-2 px-4 font-medium">Custom Reports</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-2 px-4 font-medium">API Access</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-2 px-4 font-medium">Compliance Audit</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅*</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-2 px-4 font-medium">Predictive Analytics</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">✅</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td><td class="py-2 px-2">⚠️</td><td class="py-2 px-2">❌</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">*Requires configuration, plugins, or technical expertise.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Revenue & Business Analytics</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      For experts and training businesses, learning metrics must connect to business outcomes. <strong>Thinkific TCommerce</strong> provides comprehensive revenue analytics — sales by product, cohort retention, refund rates, and subscription health. The dashboard connects learner engagement to purchase behavior, showing which content drives upgrades and renewals.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      <strong>Kajabi</strong> excels at unified business intelligence, tracking the entire customer lifecycle from email open to course completion to upsell conversion. <strong>Teachable</strong> offers solid revenue reporting with affiliate tracking and coupon performance. <strong>LearnWorlds</strong> provides detailed sales analytics plus the ability to track user segments and their learning-to-purchase correlation.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Enterprise platforms treat revenue as secondary. <strong>Docebo</strong> and <strong>Absorb</strong> offer commerce modules with basic sales reporting, but the focus is on learning administration rather than revenue optimization.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Analytics requirements should drive platform selection more than they typically do. If you need to demonstrate training ROI to executive stakeholders, enterprise platforms provide the audit trails and compliance reporting that satisfy regulators and boards. If you're optimizing a learning business for revenue and retention, expert-focused platforms connect learning data to purchase behavior more effectively.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      The gap between basic completion tracking and predictive analytics is massive — and often invisible during vendor demos. Ask specific questions: Can I track video drop-off by timestamp? Can I create custom reports without IT support? Can I export raw data to our data warehouse? The answers separate platforms that support data-driven decisions from those that merely collect data.
    </p>
  </section>

